<p>Kraken was founded by Jesse Powell in 2011 with the goal to "accelerate the adoption of cryptocurrency so that you and the rest of the world can achieve financial freedom and inclusion"<sup><a href="https://www.kraken.com/why-kraken">1</a></sup>. Kraken provides access to trading Crypto through spot and Futures markets for clients with a minimum deposit around $0-$150 USD<sup><a href="https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000381846">2</a>,<a href="https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000292886-Cryptocurrency-deposit-fees-and-minimums">3</a></sup>. Kraken also provides staking services, educational content, and a developer grant program.</p>